snippet.title: I Was Not Ready Da | Official Trailer | Aravind SA
snippet.description:
Imagine two flowers pollinating on screen for 75 minutes, with your eyes open of course - Welcome to Aravind SA's "I Was Not Ready Da"! 
This is that show that the whole family should watch - just not together. From his teenage love for white people and chatrooms, to his all inclusive approach to strip clubs in America, SA walks us through many such contradictions of traumatising languages tutors, to provoking news anchors in their own shows. 

Now, meet SA the man who is ‘finally ready’ to tell you about the times life threw shit, and he hilariously took the hit.

Releasing this Friday, 27th November 2020 on Amazon Prime Video!

Written, Performed and Directed by Aravind SA 
DoP: Srinivasan V.

snippet.title: Baap Ka Biyaah - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Papaji hain lonely aur Amit hai unka only son.Beta jawaan ho gaya hai but papa wants a companion for life. Dosari taraf Amit ki girlfriend bhi hona chahati hai uski wife.Is sabke beech phansi hui hai Amit ki jaan; aur tabhi life mein aa jati hai Miss Santosh jo hai Papa ki bhooli bisri girlfriend aur abhi tak hai single jiske sath Papa karna chahate hain mingle. Kya dad ko milegi unki dulhaniya? Kya Papa ke sath Amit ka ghar bhi basega ya vo kisi aur chakkar mein phansega? Is parivarik comedy mein mil jayenge saare jawaab. To baap ke biha mein jalool jalool aana aur like, share, comment karke jana.

snippet.title: Dua Lipa - ‘Levitating’ at the AMAs 2020
snippet.description:
Get tickets for Dua Lipa's Studio 2054 👉🏼  https://dualipa.co/Studio2054-General... 👈🏼  a kaleidoscopic rocket fuelled journey through time, space, mirror-balls, roller discos, bucket hats, belting beats, throbbing bass-lines and an absolute slam dunk of the best times in global club culture throughout the decades.

Taken from her second studio album 'Future Nostalgia' released in 2020, which featured the hit singles 'Don't Start Now', 'Physical', 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' & 'Levitating'

Get the album Future Nostalgia : https://dualipa.co/futurenostalgia

Subscribe to the Dua Lipa channel for all the best and latest official music videos, behind the scenes and live performances. 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-J-...

https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list...

Listen to more from the album 'Future Nostalgia' :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list...

Follow Dua Lipa:
Instagram:  https://dualipa.co/instagram
Facebook: http://dualipa.co/facebook
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dualipaofficial
Twitter: http://dualipa.co/twitter
YouTube: https://dualipa.co/youtube

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'. 

#DuaLipa #Levitating #FutureNostalgia

snippet.title: The Weeknd - Alone Again (Official Live Performance) | Vevo
snippet.description:
The Weeknd - Alone Again |  Vevo Official Live Performance

The Weeknd's 'After Hours' is one of those albums that paints vivid pictures. Abel Tesfaye's music has a dark radiance that's both dreamy and eerie, and the record's videos flaunt their sensuality with a macabre grace. So we were thrilled to work with the singer and their team on three exclusive performances from the 'After Hours' song list. We're kicking off our roll-out with "Alone Again." Be here tomorrow and Wednesday for "In Your Eyes" and "Faith."

snippet.description:

Buy a CD here: https://ninjasexparty.bandcamp.com/

Hey there, baby, we met out on the dance floor
You pressed your body up against me all night long
I know what’s on your mind
Our souls are entwined
In a passionate embrace
The look in your eyes
Says “Take me tonight”
Well I’ve got just the place
A place where we can be alone
Unless my mom and dad are home

Welcome to my parents’ house 
My mom left out some snackies
I bet your feeling horny now
So why don’t we get nasty

Hush now baby
You seem like a keeper
But your high heels are so loud
My dad is a light sleeper 
I’ve got my very own room
And tons of free food
What’s your favorite juice?
We’ve got mango and apple and guava and apple
So many fuckin’ fruits
My mom buys pizza rolls for me
Can you believe this shit is free?

Welcome to my parents’ house
A king must have his castle
That’s my grandma’s basset hound
He’s such a sassy rascal.
Aren’t you, Marvin?
::Woof::
Shhhh!

Parents’ house
Parents’ house

We’re gonna bring the funk tonight
I’m getting the top bunk tonight
Drop and thump that junk tonight
Like a 360 dunk tonight
Mom’s cake is chocolate chunk tonight
This party’s getting crunk tonight
We’re sparkin’ up that skunk tonight
Cause I’m your disco hunk tonight

Welcome to my parents’ house
Welcome to my parents’ house

Let’s use our inside voices
::Woof::
SHHHHH!!!!
Sometimes my mom just hangs around
To make sure I make good choices
HIT IT!

Welcome to my parents’ house

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'. 

#DuaLipa #Levitating #FutureNostalgia

Hi I’m Rick Shiels, welcome to my channel RickShielsPGAGolf. This YouTube channel is designed to help you play better golf, also to help you enjoy your golf more! 

I specialise in golf club reviews, golf club unboxing, golf club news, golf club head to heads, and all about golf clubs. 

I also want to make you play better golf by providing coaching video on all topics about golf, how to fix your slice, fix your hook, help you drive the golf ball longer, hit your irons more pure, hit your irons closer to the hole and help you draw and fade your golf shots. 
I will also help you lower your score by chipping better by stopping you duff and thin chips, pitch the ball closer and also create backspin. Also I will provide you help to putt better and hole more putts! 

On this channel I also make fun and entertaining golf content based on crazy and sometimes “gimmicky” golf clubs. I like to cut through the marketing hype about products and I like to give you the honest truth about golf equipment. 

If you enjoy the channel make sure you hit subscribe and also tap the notification bell so that you are always notified when I release a new video.

snippet.title: The Weeknd - Alone Again (Official Live Performance) | Vevo
snippet.description:
The Weeknd - Alone Again |  Vevo Official Live Performance

The Weeknd's 'After Hours' is one of those albums that paints vivid pictures. Abel Tesfaye's music has a dark radiance that's both dreamy and eerie, and the record's videos flaunt their sensuality with a macabre grace. So we were thrilled to work with the singer and their team on three exclusive performances from the 'After Hours' song list. We're kicking off our roll-out with "Alone Again." Be here tomorrow and Wednesday for "In Your Eyes" and "Faith."

snippet.title: Precision Farming Free DLC: Release Date Teaser
snippet.description:
We tell you the release date for the Precision Farming Free DLC - coming soon to Farming Simulator 19 on PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One!

More about Precision Farming on our blog!
► https://farming-simulator.com/newsArticle.php?&news_id=195

This EIT Food activity has received funding from the European Institute of Innovation and Technology (EIT), a body of the European Union, under Horizon2020, the EU Framework Programme for Research and Innovation. 

EIT Food is Europe’s leading agri-food innovation initiative, with the aim to create a sustainable and future-proof food sector. The initiative is made up of a consortium of key industry players, start-ups, research centres and universities from across Europe. EIT Food aims to collaborate closely with consumers to develop new knowledge and technology-based products and services that will ultimately deliver a healthier and more sustainable lifestyle for all European citizens.

snippet.title: 【金馬57慶功】李國煌一秒逗樂李安！喊話拍片、主持「免付費」
snippet.description:
第57屆金馬獎順利落幕，《男兒王》獲最佳造型設計肯定，新加坡喜劇天王 #李國煌 雖鎩羽而歸，仍對這次來參加金馬充滿感謝！李安導演典禮後跑滿各大慶功宴，來到《男兒王》場子被國煌哥的幽默逗笑。

國煌哥趁機邀片，還笑說明年願意來主持金馬，兩樣都是「免付費」。李安則阿莎力表示會記得這兩件事，笑說：「那你也要記得這一件事（指免付費）。」

snippet.title: Aku Bidadari Syurgamu - Aishah | #SFMM35
snippet.description:
Antara acara yang dinanti-nantikan saban tahun terutamanya buat peminat serta penggiat seni muzik tanah air. Di sinilah pentas penentuan untuk 30 lagu yang telah berjaya mara ke pusingan Muzik Muzik 35 Separuh Akhir dalam perjuangan tahunan ke acara kemuncak Anugerah Juara Lagu.

Lagu manakah yang akan layak ke AJL 35? Nantikan siaran langsung Muzik Muzik 35 Separuh Akhir (SFMM35) di saluran YouTube TV3Malaysia yang akan diadakan selama 3 hari berturut-turut bermula 20 November (Jumaat) sehingga 22 November (Ahad) pada jam 9 malam.

Berikut lagu-lagu yang akan dipertandingkan:

snippet.title: Barack Obama: The 2020 60 Minutes interview
snippet.description:
The former president shares the advice he would give President Trump, his thoughts on the killing of George Floyd, and what's behind the divisions in Washington and across the U.S. Scott Pelley reports. https://cbsn.ws/3kyvQRG

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: 52歲準影帝李國煌讚嘆大同電鍋神奇功能 見入圍證書秒掉淚 #金馬獎禮品開箱 | 台灣 蘋果新聞網
snippet.description:
52歲新加坡喜劇天王李國煌以《男兒王》首度提名金馬影帝，他來台隔離出關後住進大會安排的飯店，並收到一大箱號稱重達20公斤的貴賓禮品。《蘋果新聞網》記者陪他開箱，限量版金色大同電鍋讓他研究一番，因為他說新加坡沒這類電鍋，為之讚嘆；最驚訝是他突然打開一本精美典雅設計的冊子，是他的金馬影帝入圍證書，他在沒心理準備下當場飆淚，說是入行32年的「電影人的夢」。

他一打開發現是入圍證書，看得入神，直說：「這個（指入圍影帝證書）每年只發5張，是再怎麼努力讀書和用力賺錢都拿不到的。」他原本開箱各式禮品還笑嘻嘻，頓時一度說不出話，紅眼眶溢出淚來，連一旁老婆和經紀人都訝異他的感動真性情。

snippet.title: 林俊傑 JJ Lin《暫時的記號 Passing Through》Official Music Video
snippet.description:
暫時有多短 永恆有多長
每個永恆的自我 都只是時間暫時的記號 
但每個暫時的念頭 卻能牽動永恆的脈動

之於世界，這一生，如此渺小
相互聚集或分離，仰頭大笑或哭泣
這一刻 那一秒 都將翻動永恆的去向

葛大為透過情感面的抉擇取捨，「每個一念之間便是無窮宇宙」，將整個宏偉的宇宙觀放入歌曲裡面，整張專輯從廣大與無限的總結導出。人生之於永恆，不過是短暫的歲月，然而，想成為怎樣的記號，正是JJ想透過這首歌誘發深思的問句。
當每個念想都只是時間流裡短暫的記號，那麼或許也該學著在生命這個開放式系統中懂得放下限制與執著，去接受各種不同的發生。

人的記憶通常停留在一段過程的某一個瞬間，是暫時，也是永恆。

MV 聚焦於歌曲的意境與意義，再度邀請余靜萍擔任導演，余靜萍將角色從平面攝影師到動態影像攝影師，進而延伸至MV導演，透過各種面向與方式參與這張專輯的概念，善於用畫面說故事的她選擇跳脫MV的概念並採用他最擅長的方式，用大量的平面照片說故事。以不同故事線堆疊的片段組合而成，傳達了不同狀態、不同階段的人生，每一刻的情感都是全世界，而這些片段將牽引著最終的去處。而導演安排JJ用同一個身分從倖存者貫穿來到這支MV，將情感與理念繼續延續下去。然而最後這些MV中的角色也都跟JJ站在一起望向同一個地方，故事價值回到每一個人身上，體現了整張專輯的概念。

#林俊傑暫時的記號
#JJ林俊傑倖存者如你
#JJDrifterLikeYouDo 
#JJXIV #JJDoubleEP
_
暫時的記號     詞：葛大為  曲：林俊傑

陽光並不普照 
什麼都看不到 
攤在手中的 
反而虛無飄渺 
 
試論誰不孤傲 
容不下結局 太跳躍 
卻把餘生鋪成 雷同的軌道 
 
每次當我沾染了 黑暗的色調 
想像自己 有對照 
在此刻 在某處 那個我 他很好 
 
每次當我迷惑在 眼前的美好 
提醒自己 更善良 
這一生 只是永恆 暫時的記號 
 
人的心很奇妙 
越寂寞越喧囂 
抉擇 讓你得到 幸福  
也帶來煩惱 
 
表象只是通道 
喜或悲最終 同樣單調 
我們只是旅程 其中的一條 
 
每次當我沾染了 黑暗的色調 
想像自己 有對照 
在此刻 在某處 那個我 他很好 
 
每次當我迷惑在 眼前那些美好 
提醒自己 更善良 
這一生 只是永恆 暫時的記號 
 
存在的 逝去的 故事線 都很像 
在終點 還會再遇到 
各種我 各自在 各宇宙 個別哭或笑 
都在這一秒 
 
每次當我沾染了 黑暗的色調 
想像自己 有對照 
在此刻 在某處 那個我 他很好 
 
每次當我迷惑在 眼前那些美好 
提醒自己 更善良 
這一生 只是永恆 暫時的記號 
身為我 只是時間 暫時的記號 
_

#JJDrifterLikeYouDo 
#JJXIV #JJDoubleEP
_
暫時的記號     詞：葛大為  曲：林俊傑

陽光並不普照 
什麼都看不到 
攤在手中的 
反而虛無飄渺 
 
試論誰不孤傲 
容不下結局 太跳躍 
卻把餘生鋪成 雷同的軌道 
 
每次當我沾染了 黑暗的色調 
想像自己 有對照 
在此刻 在某處 那個我 他很好 
 
每次當我迷惑在 眼前的美好 
提醒自己 更善良 
這一生 只是永恆 暫時的記號 
 
人的心很奇妙 
越寂寞越喧囂 
抉擇 讓你得到 幸福  
也帶來煩惱 
 
表象只是通道 
喜或悲最終 同樣單調 
我們只是旅程 其中的一條 
 
每次當我沾染了 黑暗的色調 
想像自己 有對照 
在此刻 在某處 那個我 他很好 
 
每次當我迷惑在 眼前那些美好 
提醒自己 更善良 
這一生 只是永恆 暫時的記號 
 
存在的 逝去的 故事線 都很像 
在終點 還會再遇到 
各種我 各自在 各宇宙 個別哭或笑 
都在這一秒 
 
每次當我沾染了 黑暗的色調 
想像自己 有對照 
在此刻 在某處 那個我 他很好 
 
每次當我迷惑在 眼前那些美好 
提醒自己 更善良 
這一生 只是永恆 暫時的記號 
身為我 只是時間 暫時的記號

snippet.description:

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk 2077 — Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In this world, consumed by neverending conflict, sometimes only an outsider will get the job done. And that's you.

Cyberpunk 2077, an open-world, action-adventure story from CD PROJEKT RED, is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PC, and Google Stadia on December 10th, 2020. The game will also be playable on Xbox Series X and PlayStation 5 consoles when available.

Pre-order now: https://www.cyberpunk.net/pre-order

About the game:
Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure story set in Night City, a megalopolis obsessed with power, glamour and body modification. You play as V, a mercenary outlaw going after a one-of-a-kind implant that is the key to immortality. You can customize your character’s cyberware, skillset and playstyle, and explore a vast city where the choices you make shape the story and the world around you.

Learn more:
https://www.cyberpunk.net 
https://www.twitter.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.facebook.com/CyberpunkGame 
https://www.instagram.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.discord.gg/CyberpunkGame
https://www.CyberpunkGame.tumblr.com

Tracks:

Title: Come Close
Created by: Sebastian Robertson and Daniel Davies

Title: Suicide
Created by: Geno Lenardo feat. Valin "ZEALE" Zamerron

Title: Makes Me Feel Better
Created by: Kevin Hastings

snippet.description:
Get tickets for Dua Lipa's Studio 2054 👉🏼  https://dualipa.co/Studio2054-General... 👈🏼  a kaleidoscopic rocket fuelled journey through time, space, mirror-balls, roller discos, bucket hats, belting beats, throbbing bass-lines and an absolute slam dunk of the best times in global club culture throughout the decades.

Taken from her second studio album 'Future Nostalgia' released in 2020, which featured the hit singles 'Don't Start Now', 'Physical', 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' & 'Levitating'

Get the album Future Nostalgia : https://dualipa.co/futurenostalgia

YouTube: https://dualipa.co/youtube

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'. 

#DuaLipa #Levitating #FutureNostalgia

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'.

snippet.title: Crew-1 Mission | Launch
snippet.description:
Coast Phase: https://youtu.be/eVB02SSeqgQ

SpaceX and NASA are targeting Sunday, November 15 for Falcon 9’s launch of Dragon’s first operational crew mission (Crew-1) to the International Space Station (ISS) from historic Launch Complex 39A (LC-39A) at NASA’s Kennedy Space Center in Florida. The instantaneous launch window opens at 7:27 p.m. EST on November 15, 00:27 UTC on November 16. Following stage separation, SpaceX will attempt to land Falcon 9’s first stage on the “Just Read the Instructions” droneship, which will be stationed in the Atlantic Ocean. The launch webcast will go live about 4 hours before liftoff. Tune in here to watch live.

snippet.title: Roda Viva | Bruno Covas e Guilherme Boulos | 23/11/2020
snippet.description:
Em edição especial, o Roda Viva recebe os dois candidatos que disputam o segundo turno nas eleições para a Prefeitura de São Paulo. São eles Bruno Covas (PSDB) e Guilherme Boulos (PSOL).

Graduado em Direito pela USP e em Economia pela PUC-SP, Bruno Covas foi eleito deputado estadual em 2006. Convidado por Geraldo Alckmin, assumiu a Secretaria do Meio Ambiente. Em 2016, integrou como vice-prefeito a chapa de João Doria. Assumiu a prefeitura em abril de 2018.

Graduado em Filosofia pela USP e especializado em Psicologia Clínica pela PUC-SP, Guilherme Boulos é coordenador nacional do Movimento dos Trabalhadores Sem Teto (MTST). Foi professor universitário e da rede pública de ensino. Em 2018, concorreu à Presidência da República.

#RodaViva

snippet.title: Dua Lipa - ‘Levitating’ at the AMAs 2020
snippet.description:
Get tickets for Dua Lipa's Studio 2054 👉🏼  https://dualipa.co/Studio2054-General... 👈🏼  a kaleidoscopic rocket fuelled journey through time, space, mirror-balls, roller discos, bucket hats, belting beats, throbbing bass-lines and an absolute slam dunk of the best times in global club culture throughout the decades.

Taken from her second studio album 'Future Nostalgia' released in 2020, which featured the hit singles 'Don't Start Now', 'Physical', 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' & 'Levitating'

Get the album Future Nostalgia : https://dualipa.co/futurenostalgia

Instagram:  https://dualipa.co/instagram
Facebook: http://dualipa.co/facebook
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dualipaofficial
Twitter: http://dualipa.co/twitter
YouTube: https://dualipa.co/youtube

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'.

snippet.localized.description:
Get tickets for Dua Lipa's Studio 2054 👉🏼  https://dualipa.co/Studio2054-General... 👈🏼  a kaleidoscopic rocket fuelled journey through time, space, mirror-balls, roller discos, bucket hats, belting beats, throbbing bass-lines and an absolute slam dunk of the best times in global club culture throughout the decades.

Taken from her second studio album 'Future Nostalgia' released in 2020, which featured the hit singles 'Don't Start Now', 'Physical', 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' & 'Levitating'

Get the album Future Nostalgia : https://dualipa.co/futurenostalgia

Subscribe to the Dua Lipa channel for all the best and latest official music videos, behind the scenes and live performances. 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-J-...

See more official videos from Dua Lipa here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list...

Listen to more from the album 'Future Nostalgia' :
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list...

Follow Dua Lipa:
Instagram:  https://dualipa.co/instagram
Facebook: http://dualipa.co/facebook
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dualipaofficial
Twitter: http://dualipa.co/twitter
YouTube: https://dualipa.co/youtube

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'. 

#DuaLipa #Levitating #FutureNostalgia

snippet.description:

snippet.title: OBJETO ESTRANHO NO CÉU? Cometa Novo? DESCUBRA o que era!
snippet.description:
Olá! Seja bem-vindo ao Astro Space, o seu canal de astrofotografia :)

Neste vídeo extra, vou falar sobre o objeto que deixou todo mundo intrigado! Recebi dezenas de mensagens sobre o que aconteceu hoje a noite e se tinha um cometa novo na área, mas na verdade estávamos falando apenas de um "Fuel Dump", processo de alijamento de combustível feito pelo foguete Chinês Long March 5, que levou hoje às 17h30 a missão CHANG'E 5 para a lua.

Conhece alguém que ficou intrigado? Mande este vídeo para ele :)

snippet.title: TODOS os videos vão monetizar no YouTube | Canal pequeno NÃO comemore 😢
snippet.description:
O Youtube vai exibir propagandas no seu vídeo, mesmo que seu canal ainda não seja monetizado, por mais que essa pareça uma ótima notícia pra quem ainda não tem mil inscritos e 4mil horas para participar do programa de parcerias do youtube (a monetização) não é uma boa notícia.

Como você e seu canal ainda não fazem parte da monetização do YouiTube, não vai receber dinheiro pelas propagandas exibidas no seu próprio video.

Informação do YouTube:
"Para canais que ainda não fazem parte do Programa de Parcerias do YouTube:
Adicionamos essa nova seção para informar você que, a partir de hoje, começaremos a exibir anúncios aos poucos em um número limitado de vídeos de canais que não fazem parte do Programa de Parcerias do YouTube. Isso significa que, como um criador de conteúdo que não gera receita, alguns anúncios podem ser exibidos no seu conteúdo. Como você não está no Programa de Parcerias do YouTube, não receberá uma parcela da receita gerada por essa publicidade."

Monetiza seu canal com 3 videos ou menos:
👉 http://monetizarcanal.com.br
--

snippet.description: Razzien, Festnahmen und zwei Flüchtige: Die Spur des spektakulären Juwelenraubs von Dresden führt offenbar zum Familien-Clan der Remmos aus Berlin. Einer von ihnen ist Wissam Remmo, der bereits für den Klau der Goldmünze aus dem Bode-Museum verantwortlich aber trotzdem auf freiem Fuß war.

LYRICS
Wenn du zu mir sagst, 
du schläfst nicht so gut
Dann weiß ich warum, 
doch geb es nicht zu, 
wie weh mir das tut
 
Ne Woche danach 
Wir sprühen vor Glück 
Bis ich dich küss
und merke, du bist
woanders als ich 
 
Weiß nicht, wie ich's ändern kann,
dass hier alles zerfällt,
doch ich halt fest daran
Belüge mich selbst 
Und ich bin wütend auf dich
Und ich bin wütend auf mich
 
Ich glaube, dass du sie noch liebst
Tu nicht so, als wär sie niemand
Du sagst, du denkst nicht mehr an sie,
aber du tust es immer wieder
 
Ich hab Angst, dich zu verlier‘n,
seit ich es zum ersten Mal, 
zum ersten Mal gespürt hab
Du sagst, du denkst nicht mehr an sie,
aber du tust es immer wieder
 
Wenn wir spazieren, 
dann kann es passieren
dass du zu mir sagst, 
wir war'n schon mal hier, 
doch das war mit ihr
 
Und wenn ich dich frag,
habt ihr noch Kontakt,
dann sagst du nicht viel
Ich hass das Gefühl 
Warum blockst du mich ab?

#LEA #DuTustEsImmerWieder

Heute haben wir Dialekt, Tradition und Autotune-Trap kombiniert.
Spotify etc: ab 31.10:
 https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/sftig/dirndl-weed-2

📸Instagram  https://www.instagram.com/saaftig/

Prod. by SÄÄFTIG
Mixing: Sääftig
Lyrics by Sääftig & 10tj10

[Hook]
Wenn Peter mit die Brüder drauß'n wieder Nasen zieht (Jo mei)
Da buff' ma mit den Madeln
In ihr'm Dirndl steckt noch Weed (Ah, uh, uh)
Saufen tun wir jeden Tag, die Maß ist immer leer
Ey, schau da hinten kommt die Gertraud, die will G'schlechtsverkehr
Wir sagen: „Hey, bufferladiey
Jokserladiejhidelihurlijoliej“
Wir singa, uhh: (Jo mei) „Buff-bufferladiey jokserladiejhirsliahurlioliej“

[Part]
Mit zwei Leberkäs, 'ner Bretz'n, ja, da is die Gaudi groß
Bin scho' wieder mies am Saufen mit zwei Mädels aufm Schoß
Morgen Mittag Weißwurstfrühstück und Abend Kloß mit Soß'
Joa, des Fleisch g'hört aufn Teller, sonst lass ich mei' Henna los
Bin am Saufen, bin am Schlafen
Ja, die Squad, die weiß Bescheid
Bin i morgens net erreichbar, ja, dann tut's mir wirklich leid
Willst du heit no' weiter feiern? Ach, die Party is vorbei
Nur der Sääftig is am Tanzen und des endet net um drei

snippet.title: Vergleich mit Sophie Scholl: Kritik an Querdenken-Rednerin | WDR Aktuelle Stunde
snippet.description:
Auf einer "Querdenken"-Demo in Hannover am Samstag hat eine Rednerin ihren Corona-Protest mit dem Aktivismus der Nazi-Widerstandskämpferin Sophie Scholl verglichen. Dieser Vergleich war dann auch einem Mann zu viel, der wohl Ordner auf der Demo war: Vor laufender Kamera warf er der Frau "Verharmlosung des Holocaust" vor, zog seine Ordner-Weste aus und ging. Für "Jana aus Kassel", wie sich die Frau vorstellt, hagelt es jetzt Kritik im Netz - auch von Bundesaußenminister Heiko Maas.

snippet.title: "Querdenker" und Co.: NS-Vergleiche sind immer falsch! | #mirkosmeinung
snippet.description:
Eine junge Frau aus Kassel vergleicht sich bei einer Demonstration gegen Corona-Maßnahmen mit Sophie Scholl. Einem 11-jährigen Mädchen legen mutmaßlich ihre Eltern kurz vorher in den Mund, sie sei sich beim Geburtstagsfeiern wie Anne Frank in ihrem Versteck vorgekommen. Immer wieder fallen „Querdenker" gerade mit Nazi-Vergleichen auf – dabei sollte eigentlich klar sein: So etwas ist total daneben. Mehr zu Mirkos Meinung gibt es in diesem Video.

Die Wikipedia-Seite zu Nazi-Vergleichen - https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nazi-Vergleich

Der „Spiegel" 1986 über Helmut Kohls Goebbels-Vergleich - https://www.spiegel.de/spiegel/print/d-13521510.html

snippet.title: Hamid sucht Porsche 911 I GRIP
snippet.description:
Hamids Auftraggeber, Berufspilot Antonio Cristofaro, hat einen besonderen Autowunsch. Der Fluglehrer ist Petrolhead durch und durch. PS-starke Sportwagen sind seine Leidenschaft. Deswegen bittet er den Luxusauto-Experten, ihm einen besonderen Neun-Elfer zu besorgen. Antonios Budget für die Porsche-Ikone: 70.000 Euro. Das Problem an diesem Auftrag: Der Wagen soll weniger als 100.000 Kilometer gelaufen sein - und eine Handschaltung besitzen! Hamid wird tatsächlich fündig: Zur Wahl stehen je ein Turbo der Baureihen 996 und 997 sowie ein 993 Targa – einer der letzten Luftgekühlten! Da sollte doch eigentlich der passende Zuffenhausener dabei sein, oder?



Abonnieren unseren Kanal: https://www.youtube.com/user/GRIPRTL2?sub_confirmation=1 
Komplette Folgen GRIP auf TV NOW: http://www.tvnow.de/rtl2/grip-das-motormagazin
Alle Infos zur Sendung: http://www.rtl2.de/sendung/grip-das-motormagazin

GRIP bei Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/grip
GRIP bei YouTube abonnieren: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=GRIPRTL2

Seit 2007 bietet „GRIP - Das Motormagazin“ seinen Zuschauern sonntags bei RTLZWEI kompetenten Motorjournalismus vereint mit Tests der Superlative. Mit viel Humor, einem hochwertigen Look und außergewöhnlichen Themen verbindet „GRIP - Das Motormagazin“ Unterhaltung rund um die Motorwelt mit Service für den Verbraucher.

Die Moderatoren Det Müller, Matthias Malmedie, Helge Thomsen, Cyndie Allemann und Niki Schelle zeigen jede Woche die heißesten Auto-Trends, wagen rasante Versuche und geben kompetente Tipps.

GRIP ist aber nicht nur im TV zu finden. So gibt es ein Printmagazin, das in der DAZ-Verlagsgruppe erscheint, Musik-Compilations in Kooperation mit Sony Music und Events wie das „GRIP - Das Motorevent“. Auch bei Youtube, Facebook und Instagram begeistert GRIP durch regelmäßig aktualisierte Inhalte die Abonnenten.

"GRIP - Das Motormagazin", immer sonntags im TV bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: Precision Farming Free DLC: Release Date Teaser
snippet.description:
We tell you the release date for the Precision Farming Free DLC - coming soon to Farming Simulator 19 on PC, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One!

More about Precision Farming on our blog!
► https://farming-simulator.com/newsArticle.php?&news_id=195

This EIT Food activity has received funding from the European Institute of Innovation and Technology (EIT), a body of the European Union, under Horizon2020, the EU Framework Programme for Research and Innovation. 

EIT Food is Europe’s leading agri-food innovation initiative, with the aim to create a sustainable and future-proof food sector. The initiative is made up of a consortium of key industry players, start-ups, research centres and universities from across Europe. EIT Food aims to collaborate closely with consumers to develop new knowledge and technology-based products and services that will ultimately deliver a healthier and more sustainable lifestyle for all European citizens.

snippet.title: Dua Lipa - ‘Levitating’ at the AMAs 2020
snippet.description:
Get tickets for Dua Lipa's Studio 2054 👉🏼  https://dualipa.co/Studio2054-General... 👈🏼  a kaleidoscopic rocket fuelled journey through time, space, mirror-balls, roller discos, bucket hats, belting beats, throbbing bass-lines and an absolute slam dunk of the best times in global club culture throughout the decades.

Taken from her second studio album 'Future Nostalgia' released in 2020, which featured the hit singles 'Don't Start Now', 'Physical', 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' & 'Levitating'

Facebook: http://dualipa.co/facebook
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@dualipaofficial
Twitter: http://dualipa.co/twitter
YouTube: https://dualipa.co/youtube

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'. 

#DuaLipa #Levitating #FutureNostalgia

snippet.title: Wird Connor Dean die Wahrheit sagen?! 😰 | Berlin - Tag & Nacht #2328
snippet.description:
Am Morgen bekommt Connor Panik und glaubt, dass Kim seinem Vater von dem Seitensprung erzählen möchte. Dabei läuft es doch mit Toni endlich wieder gut! Als er Kim daraufhin bittet, bloß nichts zu verraten, bekommt ausgerechnet Dean das mit! Ahnt er etwas?

Die gescriptete Reality-Soap „Berlin - Tag & Nacht“ zeigt die coolste WG Berlins, mit Themen wie  Freundschaft, Liebe,  Eifersucht, Affären, Glück, Freude und Leiden. Wie im echten Leben eben!
Alte wie neue WG-Bewohner, u. a. Ole, Joe, Peggy, Krätze, Schmidti, Eule, Basti Paula, Piet, Milla, Leon und viele weitere, zeigen dir ihr Leben in Berlin, der bunten Metropole Deutschlands. Sie nehmen dich mit in ihre Wohngemeinschaften, auf ihre Arbeitsplätze, in den Club Matrix, den Friseursalon „Schnitte“ sowie die Bar LA 14. Auch ein Tattoostudio und das Fitnessstudio Body Burn gehören zu den unterschiedlichen und wechselnden Handlungsorten der Serie. Die Großstadt-Soap „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“ ist nicht zuletzt deshalb so beliebt, weil sie die Bewohner der WGs im Ringen mit alltäglichen Problemen zeigt: Affäre und Eifersucht, Erfolgsdruck im Beruf sowie viele zwischenmenschliche Konflikte. 

"Berlin - Tag & Nacht" läuft Montag bis Freitag um 19:05 Uhr bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: Ein schnelles Rezept zum Mittagessen, Kartoffeln mit Fleisch, so hast du noch nicht gekocht #198
snippet.description:
Ein schnelles Rezept zum Mittagessen. Kartoffeln mit Fleisch, so hast du noch nicht gekocht und aß nicht. Ein schnelles Rezept für ein großartiges Abendessen mit Kartoffeln und Fleisch für alle. Ein einfaches Rezept für das Mittagessen, mit dem jeder umgehen kann. Kartoffel-Fleisch-Rezept, dies ist ein gesundes und leckeres Mittagsrezept. Ein schnelles Rezept für Kartoffeln mit Fleisch zum Mittagessen, es ist sehr einfach zu kochen, die Hauptsache ist, mit Liebe zu kochen.
Kochrezept und Zutaten:
2 Zwiebeln und 300 gr Pilze hacken
Bei mittlerer Hitze 7 Minuten braten
700 g Kartoffeln hacken
Salz, Pfeffer, Fett hinzufügen und weitere 5 Minuten braten
700 g Fleisch hacken, Salz und Pfeffer hinzufügen
Backform mit Butter einfetten
3 EL Sauerrahm und 1/2 EL Senf
200 Gramm Käse reiben
Mit Folie abdecken und 50 Minuten bei 180 ° C backen
weitere 10 Minuten backen
guten Appetit

localizations.ko.title: 빠른 점심 레시피, 고기가 들어간 감자, 당신은 이렇게 요리하지 않았습니다 # 198
localizations.ko.description:
점심을위한 빠른 조리법. 당신은 그런 고기로 감자를 요리하지 않았고 먹지도 않았습니다. 모두를위한 훌륭한 감자와 고기 저녁 식사를위한 빠른 조리법. 누구나 다룰 수있는 간단한 런치 레시피. 감자와 고기 요리법, 이것은 건강하고 맛있는 점심 요리법입니다. 점심 식사를 위해 고기를 곁들인 감자에 대한 빠른 요리법은 요리하기가 매우 쉽고 가장 중요한 것은 사랑으로 요리하는 것입니다.
조리법 및 재료 :
양파 2 개와 버섯 300g을 자릅니다.
중불에서 7 분간 볶습니다.
감자 700g 자르기
소금, 후추, 지방을 넣고 5 분 더 볶습니다.
고기 700g을 자르고 소금과 후추를 넣으십시오.
베이킹 팬에 버터를 바릅니다.
사워 크림 3 큰술과 겨자 1/2 큰술
치즈 200g을 갈아서
호일로 덮고 180 ° C에서 50 분 동안 굽습니다.
10 분 더 굽습니다
맛있게 드세요
친구, 비디오가 마음에 들면 채널을 도울 수 있습니다.
📢이 비디오를 소셜 네트워크에서 친구들과 공유하십시오. 네트워크 + 레시피가 사이트에 저장됩니다!

A quick recipe for lunch. Potatoes with meat, you haven't cooked that way and haven't eaten. A quick recipe for a great potato and meat dinner for everyone. A simple lunch recipe that anyone can handle. Potato and meat recipe, this is a healthy and delicious lunch recipe. A quick recipe for potatoes with meat for lunch, it is very easy to cook, the main thing is to cook with love.
Cooking recipe and ingredients:
Chop 2 onions and 300 grams of mushrooms
Fry for 7 minutes over medium heat
Chop 700 g potatoes
Add salt, pepper, fat and fry for another 5 minutes
Chop 700 g of meat, add salt and pepper
Grease the baking pan with butter
3 tbsp sour cream and 1/2 tbsp mustard
Grate 200 grams of cheese
Cover with foil and bake for 50 minutes at 180 ° C
Bake for another 10 minutes
Enjoy your meal

localizations.ja.title: 簡単なランチレシピ、肉入りポテト、あなたはこのように調理していません＃198
localizations.ja.description:
ランチの簡単なレシピ。あなたはそのような肉でジャガイモを調理したことがなく、食べたことがありません。みんなのための素晴らしいポテトと肉のディナーのための簡単なレシピ。誰でも扱えるシンプルなランチレシピ。ポテトと肉のレシピ、これは健康的でおいしいランチレシピです。昼食に肉を使ったジャガイモの簡単なレシピは、調理がとても簡単です。主なことは愛を込めて調理することです。
調理レシピと材料：
玉ねぎ2個とキノコ300グラムを切る
中火で7分間炒める
700gのジャガイモを切る
塩、コショウ、脂肪を加え、さらに5分間炒める
700 gの肉を切り刻み、塩とコショウを加える
ベーキングパンにバターを塗る
大さじ3のサワークリームと大さじ1/2のマスタード
200グラムのチーズをすりおろす
ホイルで覆い、180°Cで50分間焼きます
さらに10分間焼きます
どうぞお召し上がりください

En simpel frokostopskrift, som alle kan klare. Kartoffel- og kødopskrift, dette er en sund og lækker frokostopskrift. En hurtig opskrift på kartofler med kød til frokost, det er meget let at lave mad, det vigtigste er at lave mad med kærlighed.
Madlavningsopskrift og ingredienser:
Hak 2 løg og 300 gram svampe
Steg i 7 minutter på medium varme
Hak 700 g kartofler
Tilsæt salt, peber, fedt og steg i yderligere 5 minutter
Hak 700 g kød, tilsæt salt og peber
Smør bagepladen med smør
3 spsk creme fraiche og 1/2 spsk sennep
Riv 200 gram ost
Dæk med folie og bages i 50 minutter ved 180 ° C
Bages i yderligere 10 minutter
Nyd dit måltid
Venner, hvis du kunne lide videoen, kan du hjælpe kanalen:
📢 Del denne video med dine venner på sociale netværk. Netværk + opskrift gemmes på dit websted!
RANGER VIDEOEN! 👍 - det er behageligt for mig og vigtigt for udviklingen af ​​kanalen!
  SKRIV EN KOMMENTAR eller i det mindste et smilende ansigt. Det er ikke svært for dig, men jeg bliver meget glad!

localizations.hu.title: Gyors ebéd recept, burgonya hússal, még nem főzted így # 198
localizations.hu.description:
Gyors recept ebédre. Nem főtt ilyen hússal burgonyát, és nem evett. Gyors recept egy remek krumpli- és húsvacsorához mindenkinek. Egyszerű ebéd recept, amelyet bárki kezelhet. Burgonya és hús recept, ez egy egészséges és finom ebéd recept. Gyors recept burgonyával, hússal ebédre, nagyon könnyű főzni, a lényeg az, hogy szeretettel főzzünk.
Főzés receptje és összetevői:
Vágj fel 2 hagymát és 300 gramm gombát
7 percig sütjük közepes lángon
Vágjon 700 g burgonyát
Sózzuk, borsozzuk, zsírozzuk és további 5 percig sütjük
Vágjon 700 g húst, adjon hozzá sót és borsot
Kenje meg a tepsit vajjal
3 evőkanál tejföl és 1/2 ek mustár
200 gr sajtot reszeljünk le
Fedjük le fóliával és süssük 50 percig 180 ° C-on
Süssük még 10 percig
Jó étvágyat

localizations.sq.title: Një recetë e shpejtë dreke, patate me mish, nuk e keni gatuar si kjo # 198
localizations.sq.description:
Një recetë e shpejtë dreke. Ju nuk keni gatuar patate me mish të tillë dhe nuk keni ngrënë. Një recetë e shpejtë për një darkë të mrekullueshme me patate dhe mish për të gjithë. Një recetë e thjeshtë dreke që çdokush mund ta trajtojë. Recetë patate dhe mishi, kjo është një recetë e shëndetshme dhe e shijshme e drekës. Një recetë e shpejtë për patate me mish për drekë, është shumë e lehtë për tu gatuar, gjëja kryesore është të gatuash me dashuri.
Receta e gatimit dhe përbërësit:
Prisni 2 qepë dhe 300 gram kërpudha
Skuqini për 7 minuta në nxehtësi mesatare
Prisni 700 g patate
Shtoni kripë, piper, yndyrë dhe skuqni për 5 minuta të tjera
Prisni 700 g mish, shtoni kripë dhe piper
Lyejmë tavën për pjekje me gjalpë
3 tbsp salcë kosi dhe 1/2 tbsp mustardë
Grijmë 200 gram djathë
E mbulojmë me letër varaku dhe e pjekim për 50 minuta në 180 ° C
Piqni edhe 10 minuta
Të bëftë mirë
Miq, nëse ju ka pëlqyer videoja, mund të ndihmoni kanalin:
📢 Ndani këtë video me miqtë tuaj në rrjetet sociale. Rrjeti + receta do të ruhet në faqen tuaj!
👍 Vlerësoni VIDEO! 👍 - kjo është e këndshme për mua dhe e rëndësishme për zhvillimin e kanalit!
  SHKRUAJ KOMENT, ose të paktën një fytyrë buzëqeshëse. Nuk është e vështirë për ju, por unë do të jem shumë e lumtur!

localizations.cs.title: Rychlý recept na oběd, brambory s masem, takto jste nevařili # 198
localizations.cs.description:
Rychlý recept na oběd. S masem jste takhle nevařili brambory a nejedli jste. Rychlý recept na skvělou bramborovou a masovou večeři pro každého. Jednoduchý recept na oběd, který zvládne každý. Recept na brambory a maso, toto je zdravý a lahodný recept na oběd. Rychlý recept na brambory s masem na oběd, je velmi snadné vařit, hlavní je vařit s láskou.
Recept na vaření a přísady:
Nakrájejte 2 cibule a 300 gramů hub
Smažte 7 minut na středním ohni
Nakrájejte 700 g brambor
Přidejte sůl, pepř, tuk a smažte dalších 5 minut
Nakrájejte 700 g masa, přidejte sůl a pepř
Pekáč vymastíme máslem
3 lžíce zakysané smetany a 1/2 lžíce hořčice
Nastrouhejte 200 gramů sýra
Zakryjte fólií a pečte 50 minut při 180 ° C
Pečte dalších 10 minut
Dobrou chuť

localizations.hr.title: Recept za brzi ručak, krumpir s mesom, niste kuhali na ovaj način # 198
localizations.hr.description:
Brzi recept za ručak. Niste kuhali krumpir s takvim mesom i niste jeli. Brzi recept za izvrsnu večeru od krumpira i mesa za sve. Jednostavan recept za ručak s kojim se svatko može nositi. Recept za krumpir i meso, ovo je zdrav i ukusan recept za ručak. Brzi recept za krumpir s mesom za ručak, vrlo je jednostavno kuhati, glavna stvar je kuhati s ljubavlju.
Recept i sastojci za kuhanje:
Nasjeckajte 2 glavice luka i 300 grama gljiva
Pržite 7 minuta na umjerenoj vatri
Nasjeckajte 700 g krumpira
Dodajte sol, papar, mast i pržite još 5 minuta
Nasjeckajte 700 g mesa, dodajte sol i papar
Podmažite tepsiju maslacem
3 žlice kiselog vrhnja i 1/2 žlice senfa
Naribajte 200 grama sira
Pokriti folijom i peći 50 minuta na 180 ° C
Pecite još 10 minuta
Uživajte u jelu

localizations.pl.title: Szybki przepis na lunch, ziemniaki z mięsem, tak nie gotowałeś # 198
localizations.pl.description:
Szybki przepis na obiad. Nie gotowałeś ziemniaków z takim mięsem i nie jadłeś. Szybki przepis na wspaniały obiad ziemniaczano-mięsny dla każdego. Prosty przepis na lunch, z którym każdy sobie poradzi. Przepis na ziemniaki i mięso, to zdrowy i pyszny przepis na lunch. Szybki przepis na ziemniaki z mięsem na lunch, bardzo łatwo jest ugotować, najważniejsze jest gotowanie z miłością.
Przepis na gotowanie i składniki:
Posiekaj 2 cebule i 300 gramów grzybów
Smażyć przez 7 minut na średnim ogniu
Posiekaj 700 g ziemniaków
Dodaj sól, pieprz, tłuszcz i smaż przez kolejne 5 minut
Posiekaj 700 g mięsa, dodaj sól i pieprz
Smarujemy blachę do pieczenia masłem
3 łyżki śmietany i 1/2 łyżki musztardy
Zetrzyj 200 gramów sera
Przykryj folią i piecz przez 50 minut w temperaturze 180 ° C
Piecz jeszcze 10 minut
Smacznego
Przyjaciele, jeśli podobał Ci się film, możesz pomóc kanałowi:
📢 Udostępnij ten film znajomym w sieciach społecznościowych. Przepis Network + zostanie zapisany na Twojej stronie!
👍 OCEŃ WIDEO! 👍 - to dla mnie przyjemne i ważne dla rozwoju kanału!

snippet.title: Brawl Stars Animation: Season 4 - Holiday Getaway!
snippet.description:
Download NOW!! ►► https://supr.cl/playbrawl
Be a BRAWLER! Subscribe! ►► https://supr.cl/subscribe

Fast-paced 3v3 multiplayer and battle royale made for mobile! Play with friends or solo across a variety of game modes in under three minutes.

Unlock and upgrade dozens of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Collect unique skins to stand out and show off. Battle in a variety of mysterious locations within the Brawliverse!

BATTLE IN MULTIPLE GAME MODES
- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.
- Showdown (Solo/Duo): A battle royale style fight for survival. Collect power ups for your Brawler. Grab a friend or play solo - be the last Brawler standing in the rowdiest battle royale yet. Winner take all!
- Brawl Ball (3v3): It's a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team’s safe and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.
- Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!

UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS
Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skins.

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
